:: EXAMPLE `dateRange` input structure in Analytics streams:
    {
        "dateRange": {
            "start": {"month": 8, "day": 13, "year": 2021},
            "end": {"month": 8, "day": 13, "year": 2021}
        }
    }
:: EXAMPLE output:
    {
        "start_date": "2021-08-13",
        "end_date": "2021-08-13"
    }

